{
  "stem": "11067.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And of course, I was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "We got off the boat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And we were put into a huge room, told to get our luggage, and wait till our names to be called.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "German.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that point, German was used.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were kids around me who were crying.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had found my suitcase.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember telling them to sit on my suitcase and I would find theirs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we waited a few hours, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And our names were called.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Our names being three others and mine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were met by two gentlemen who also didn't speak German.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were told to go with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were-- we went with them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we went on a train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The other three kids thought this was very funny, and were kind of rambunctious.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was being mother to them, and telling them they had to sit quietly, and they had to behave.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we reached our destination, which was Kenilworth in the midlands of England, near a town of Coventry.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "One of the gentlemen's name was Sidney Laxon.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was a member of the Christadelphian ecclesia in Coventry.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Christadelphians are a sect of people, very fundamental, brothers in Christ.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Turns out that they established hostels for refugees.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they took us into their homes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Sidney Laxon was particularly benevolent, shall we say.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He had a lovely estate in Kenilworth.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And there was sort of the first glimmer that things were not going to be bad-- that they were OK.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He already had a refugee from Prague.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "She had been with him a couple of months, spoke some English, translated for us, and said, in essence, it's OK guys, you're now fine.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Her name was Gretel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And for some reason her last name has escaped me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I've lost track of her.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
